=== bare (usage) ===
mastodon - a Fediverse/Mastodon CLI client for AmigaOS

Usage:
  mastodon timeline              show the home (or public) timeline
  mastodon post "text"           post a status ("toot")

Options:
  --host NAME         instance host, e.g. mastodon.social
  --proxy host:port   use the plain-HTTP host bridge (no AmiSSL)
  --insecure          skip TLS certificate verification
  -v, --verbose       print transport progress
  -h, --help          this help

Token: put a bearer token in SYS:.mastodon/token. Needed for the
home timeline and for posting; the public timeline works without one.
